Hello again.  /sigh.  Another scam to report to you here.  I don't think many will fall for this one as one look at the spelling alone should bring up warning signs.<BR>Auric.<P> <BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR><font face="Verdana, Arial" size="2"><BR>GM Dayswan<BR>poon<BR>(8/15/01 8:37:44 am)<BR>Reply  Verant [EDITED] me im gonna [EDITED] them<BR>-----------------------------------------------------------------------<BR> I am a GM on Sullon Zek server. I am quitting EQ couse Verant has screwed me over by deleating my other account due to someone saying that i have been getting him twinked by other GM's and now i am on investigation. Well I am gunna screw Verant befor i get kicked off the game, if you want any item for you character I can get it for you. Go to <A HREF="http://www.[EDITED].com" TARGET=_blank>www.[EDITED].com</A> and make a account there. then send me a message (EDITED) to GMDayswan with you Login Name and Password. then give me a list of what you want on your character and I shall get it for you. Anyways Dark Age Of Camelot is going to be out soon and I am gunna start playing that Instead couse it looks better and It wont be as corrupt as EverQuest. <P>Thanks GM Dayswon  <BR></font><HR></BLOCKQUOTE><BR>

