Please allow me to add a note to this.<P>I am the Lead Tester for EverQuest and I would never ask for anyone's password over an email.  I am also the main contact for our department with the public.<P>If you ever get an email from someone claiming to be a tester for EQ please do not hesitate to email me and check the authenticity of the email.  I am esauter@station.sony.com<BR>I will be more than happy to confirm any questionable email.<P>Thanks everyone!!<P>Ester the Tester

